<plot>Five friends spend a winter weekend at a rustic cottage. When one of them is found dead, the remaining four create their own disturbed reality in a desperate attempt to control the situation. They become lost in a world of delusion inhabited by dead technology and primal lust. As another reality asserts itself, we discover what awaits them, and that they are not alone.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?577125</url></doc>
